data.value:
OpenGL Solar System Simulator =============================
Written by Sergey Safarov.
This is the C++ port of my old University labwork written with Delphi.
You can move around the system and make nice views from the any points.
=============================
Controls
W - move camera FORWARD S - move camera BACKWARD A - slide camera LEFT D - slide camera RIGHT Q - turn camera LEFT E - turn camera RIGHT
I - pitch camera UP K - pitch camera DOWN J - roll camera COUNTERCLOCKWISE L - roll camera CLOCKWISE
` - global lightswitch :) g - beta glow effect which is represent by diferent fogs
, - decrease camera movement speed . - increase camera movement speed
Feel free to write me about anything touches this project and other opportunities!
Enjoy and have a nice day!
